## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The rapid evolution of social media platforms means that the information could become outdated quickly. Additionally, the analysis primarily focuses on the positive aspects of social media communication, with less emphasis on potential negative impacts. Further research could explore these areas in more depth to provide a balanced view.

